# 🚀 Sales Data Automation Pipeline

An end-to-end sales reporting automation pipeline built using **n8n**, **MySQL**, **SQL**, **Docker**, and **SMTP**. This project automates the complete process of uploading sales data, analyzing it, generating reports, sending them via email, and preparing the database for the next execution.

---

## 📌 Project Overview

This project demonstrates an ETL (Extract, Transform, Load) workflow using **n8n**.

The workflow accepts a CSV file through an n8n Form Trigger, extracts the data, stores it in a MySQL database, performs SQL-based analytics, generates a formatted sales report, emails the report automatically, and finally clears the database to prepare for the next upload.

---

## 🚀 Workflow

```text
Upload Sales CSV
        │
        ▼
Extract Data from CSV
        │
        ▼
Insert Data into MySQL
        │
        ▼
Execute SQL Analytics
        │
        ▼
Generate Sales Report
        ├────────► Send Email
        │
        └────────► Clear Sales Data
```

---

## ✨ Features

- Upload sales data through an n8n Form
- Automatically extract CSV records
- Store data in MySQL
- Execute SQL analytics
- Calculate Total Sales
- Calculate Total Orders
- Calculate Average Order Value
- Find Top Selling Product
- Generate Region-wise Sales Report
- Generate Product-wise Revenue Report
- Generate Daily Sales Report
- Automatically email the report
- Clear the database after execution
- Docker-based deployment

